use two pointer method-logic
step1:declare i and j two variable for iterate the two list.i for first array list and j for second array list
step2:declare another variable k to store the sorted list.
step3:compare i and j
    while i<len(list1) and j<len(list2):
    if i<j:
        k.append(list1[i])
    else:
        k.append(list2[j]
step4:return the k.
                 


